- **Court fee:** £355
- **Legal costs:** £1,000-£3,000 (estimated)
- **Bailiff costs:** £130 (if enforcement needed)
- **Interest on arrears:** {{interest_rate}}% per annum
- **Total estimated:** £{{estimated_total_costs}}

